590
00:37:09,230 --> 00:37:10,600
Seems like a perfect match.

591
00:37:11,800 --> 00:37:13,330
That's it for today.
Thank you so much, you two.

592
00:37:13,360 --> 00:37:14,880
Thank you.

593
00:37:20,540 --> 00:37:21,500
Wow!

594
00:37:21,540 --> 00:37:22,300
Thank you.

595
